    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v2
    v0 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.47) * (v1 + 0.31 / v2 + 0.74)) + (0.17 * 0.81))
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.sin((tmp + 0.72 + tmp + 0.85)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.sin((v1 + 0.54 * v2 + 0.28)))
    v2 = (tmp + 0.22)
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v1 + 0.62)) + wp.abs(0.85))
    v2 = ((v2 - 0.44) * ((v2 + 0.61 / v2 + 0.71) * (v0 + 0.32 * v0 + 0.79)))
    data[tid] = v0
